RelatedSentence: Another American vessel , the Vella Gulf , is traveling towards the Black Sea .
The  cruiser will enter the sea on the eve of presidential elections in Ukraine , scheduled for May 25 .
American diplomats stressed that the United States wanted to support the actions of the new Ukrainian authorities through the presence of US warships in the Black Sea .

The Vella Gulf is armed with Tomahawk cruise missiles , ACPOK , and antisubmarine and antiaircraft Standard - 2 and Standard - 3 missiles .
The ship carries the total of 122 missiles on board .
The vessel also has two multipurpose helicopters .
